# Place the unpacked iBeike extension files in this directory before building Docker.
#
# Steps:
# 1. Open Chrome and navigate to: chrome://extensions/
# 2. Find the iBeike (爱贝壳) extension, click "Details"
# 3. Note the extension ID: jejejajkcbhejfiocemmddgbkdlhhngm
# 4. Copy the extension folder from:
#    Windows: %LOCALAPPDATA%\Google\Chrome\User Data\Default\Extensions\jejejajkcbhejfiocemmddgbkdlhhngm\<version>\
# 5. Paste all files into this directory (extensions/ibeike/)
# 6. Verify: extensions/ibeike/manifest.json should exist
# 7. Run: docker compose build
